author: Staff Reports
title: Area Sports Calendar, 10/7/15
text: Area Sports Calendar, 10/7/15 Staff Reports Casa Grande Valley Newspapers Inc. TODAY High school cross country: Vista Grande boys and girls versus Pueblo and Sunnyside at Villago Park, 4:30 p.m. Junior college volleyball: Arizona Western at Central Arizona, 7 p.m. THURSDAY High school volleyball: Rio Rico at Casa Grande Union, 6 p.m.; Catalina at Vista Grande, 6 p.m. FRIDAY High school football: Coronado at Casa Grande Union; Tempe at Vista Grande; Mission Heights at West Phoenix; Arcadia at Maricopa; Coolidge at Combs; Fountain Hills at Florence; Santa Cruz at American Leadership. All games begin at 7 p.m. Junior college volleyball: Yavapai at Central Arizona, 7 p.m. SATURDAY Junior college cross country: Central Arizona men and women in Thunderbird Classic at Mesa Community College, 8:15 a.m. High school volleyball: Casa Grande Union at Safford, 6 p.m. High school swimming: Casa Grande Union versus North at Palm Island pool, 4 p.m. Junior college volleyball: South Mountain at Central Arizona, 7 p.m.
